data.description: Tired of walking up and down the stairs or looking for a lovely ranch home to make new memories. Then welcome to your dream home that sits on the main road with nearly an half an acre of land. This MOVE IN READY home has a NEW ROOF, NEW WATER HEATER, NEW LUXURY VINYL PLANK FLOORING, NEW PAINT,  NEW GARAGE DOOR OPENER and NEWER AIR CONDITIONING AND HEATING. The home is located within walking distances from an excellent school district. Also you won't have to worry about a strict HOA as it's not in a subdivision. As you pull into your driveway you'll feel like your home is its own oasis. First enter the foyer and then walk immediately into your family room where you can watch tv with your friends and family for football season or see yourself opening presents for the holidays in front of your gas fireplace. Next move towards the kitchen where you'll be able to cook in this spacious open concept kitchen. But if you desire more space you can easily remove the wall to combine the dining room and living room. Once you drop off your food in the kitchen walk down your hallways where you will enjoy your 3 bedrooms. The master room boast of high vaulted ceilings and a large soaking tub where you can relax after along day at work or a day full of activities. Lastly enjoy your wonderful HUGE BACK YARD!!! Where you can grill while having your friends, family and your dog running around. This land is also spacious enough to add a pool in the backyard or build a tiny home for guest or as an air b and b; create a she shed / mancave for an escape or a basic shed for additional storage items. Come schedule a showing today! This home is near Robins Air Force Base, the Aviation Museum, plenty of shops, and restaurants and easy access to the highway.
